{"tid":1246370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HA Secret既真確性有幾高?","createTime":"2019-06-20T16:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T16:28:23.000Z","uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f56316ad3f84925b02569b9c9840977cd903b9f","tid":1246370,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"前排呀陳沛然議員講左幾日<br />\n想解釋點解個病人果頭登記完呢頭就俾人拉左<br />\n一路都係想指控HA同警方之間已經有一套機制去傳送資料<br />\n<br />\n但係今日突然間HA Secret就爆左個秘密出黎<br />\n呀原來係有個RN俾警察迫佢講病人資料出黎<br />\n呀但係又唔想開名 吊撚住人胃口<br />\n講到似層層咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">突然一晚間由制度既問題 因為Secret既一篇文 變左係人既問題。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁如果係人既問題 解決方法就簡單得多 解決左個人就得了 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想大家思考下<br />\n兩邊 邊邊先係真?<br />\nSecret真確性有幾高?<br />\n定係兩邊都有可能係真? 因為有多個一個CASE?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee40d0a4ff70335b269e37527a291bcf37c3b42","tid":1246370,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"補link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2189725227816186&amp;id=731331330322257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2189725227816186%26id%3D731331330322257&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=35789123\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2189725227816186&amp;id=731331330322257</a>"}]}